@node Main "Pipeliner - Documentation"

                             'Pipeliner' 1.0

                           by Charles-N. Jacob

  'Pipeliner' is a @{" Workbench game " link play} in which you have to place
parts of various pipes in order to make a 'pipeline' from an entry
pipe, located on the upper edge, toward the exit pipe that is
located on the lower edge of the game board. When all pipes are
connected, a liquid flows from start to end...

  The more pipe sections you use to complete a pipeline, the more
points you get...

  Have fun!

